  Cancel fzf

<C-x>
  Open split

<C-v>
  Open vsplit

<C-t>
  Open tabedit

<C-o>
  Jump to buffer if already open. See :drop.
  If g:fzf_preview_buffers_jump is set to 1 then it will open the buffer in
  current window instead.

<C-q>
  Build QuickFix in open-file processes.
